name: Illustrated Map of 'Flat Earth'
description: Hand drawn map showing a version of the 'Flat Earth' model, believed by some to show the true layout of the planet. The map illustrates an number of ancient myths and includes illustrations of some ancient versions of Flat Earth maps.  This map was created purely out of interest and is in no way associated with Flat Earth theory. Very limited edition, high quality jpeg, can be printed at 50cm x 35cm.
